        transition:name="title"
        class="text-7xl font-extrabold stroke-transparent bg-gradient-primary bg-clip-text text-transparent"
      >
        LimeLimeLime
      </h1>
      <div class="max-w-md">
        <p class="py-6 text-balance">
          Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Repudiandae maiores voluptatum atque illum placeat
          totam alias, excepturi culpa, eum, quae doloremque ducimus consequatur inventore recusandae enim impedit nemo
          ipsam blanditiis?
